geBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sbt1665702732259.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sbt1665702732259.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sbt1665702732259.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sbt1665702732259\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      disable precompiler connect\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use OCI instead of precompiler interface for first logon path.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"sbt1665702732259__topic_d55577e1_d55578e1_d55579e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sbt1665702732259__p_d55580e1_d55581e1_d55582e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$ORA_PARAMS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">= disable precompiler connect</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sbt1665702732259__p_d55583e1_d55584e1_d55585e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$ORA_PARAMS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">= dpc</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sbt1665702732259__section_gly_cm4_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d588708e72\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sbt1665702732259__p_d55589e1_d55590e1_d55591e1\">This option disables the precompiler connect interface\n            and uses the Oracle Call Interface (OCI) instead. The default is\n            <var class=\"keyword varname\">on</var>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sbt1665702732259__p_d55592e1_d55593e1_d55594e1\">Uniface only creates independent non-default\n            connections using the OCI, thereby allowing user-defined 3GL to create the default\n            connection with the precompiler interface.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531899\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531899\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "disable precompiler connect Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 disable precompiler connect Use OCI instead of precompiler interface for first logon path. USYS$ORA_PARAMS = disable precompiler connect USYS$ORA_PARAMS = dpc Description This option disables the precompiler connect interface and uses the Oracle Call Interface (OCI) instead. The default is on . Uniface only creates independent non-default connections using the OCI, thereby allowing user-defined 3GL to create the default connection with the precompiler interface. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}